<%# app/views/pages/about.html.erb %>
<% content_for :title, "About — The Anchorpoint Retreat" %>
<% content_for :description, "Learn the story behind The Anchorpoint Retreat, a Colorado mountain sanctuary for corporate retreats, wellness getaways, and private gatherings." %>

<section class="section banner-home" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('dummy-img-1920x900.jpg') %>'); min-height: 50vh;">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="banner-home-container text-center">
            <h1 class="banner-home-title">Our Story</h1>
            <p class="banner-home-excerpt">The Anchorpoint Retreat — A Place to Find Your Center</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <span class="sub-heading">About Us</span>
                <h2>A Vision Brought to Life</h2>
                <p>The Anchorpoint Retreat was born from a simple belief: that the mountains have a profound power to heal, inspire, and reconnect us. After years of hosting corporate teams and wellness groups at rented venues that never quite felt right, we decided to create our own sanctuary.</p>
                <p>Every detail of the property — from the orientation of the yoga deck to catch the morning sun, to the layout of the great room designed for conversation — was intentional. We wanted a space that felt both luxurious and welcoming, where CEOs and yoga teachers alike could feel at home.</p>
                <p>Today, The Anchorpoint Retreat hosts corporate offsites, wellness retreats, family reunions, and private celebrations. We've welcomed guests from around the world and watched them leave transformed — more connected to themselves, each other, and the natural world.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-4">Our Philosophy</h3>
                <p>We believe in the power of unplugging to reconnect. In a world that's always on, we offer a place to pause. Our approach is simple: provide an extraordinary setting, handle every detail with care, and let the mountains do the rest.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <%= image_tag "dummy-img-600x600.jpg", alt: "Property Host", class: "img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3", style: "max-width: 200px;" %>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">Meet Your Host</h3>
                    <p>With over 15 years of experience in hospitality and event planning, we're dedicated to making your retreat unforgettable. We live locally and are on-site to ensure everything runs smoothly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-px-pt-small banner-service">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <h2 class="accent-color-2 text-center mb-4">Location Highlights</h2>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 grid-gap-2">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-skiing fa-3x accent-color mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">World-Class Skiing</h3>
                    <p>Minutes from Telluride Ski Resort — some of the best skiing in North America.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-water fa-3x accent-color mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">Hot Springs</h3>
                    <p>Natural hot springs within a 20-minute drive for the ultimate relaxation experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card p-4 text-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-store fa-3x accent-color mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm">Mountain Town</h3>
                    <p>Charming downtown Telluride with shops, restaurants, and galleries just minutes away.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
